    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装Hexo</p>
<p>yum install npm -y<br>npm config set registry <a href="http://registry.npm.taobao.org/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://registry.npm.taobao.org/</a><br>npm install hexo-cli -g</p>
<p>hexo init blog<br>cd blog</p>
<p>Hexo常用插件安装与配置</p>
<p>npm install hexo —save<br>npm install hexo-generator-index —save<br>npm install hexo-generator-archive —save<br>npm install hexo-generator-category —save<br>npm install hexo-generator-tag —save<br>npm install hexo-server —save<br>npm install hexo-deployer-git —save</p>
<p>cd blog<br>npm install<br>cd themes<br>git clone <a href="https://github.com/moretwo/hexo-theme.git" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/moretwo/hexo-theme.git</a> </p>
]]></content>
